assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: RVH Inc. engages in the beauty care, systems development, graphics, and solar energy businesses in Japan. It operates FLASH, an eyelash salon, which provides eyelash extension treatment services; and sells cosmetics and health food products. The company also provides FVT-air, a software for adjusting and quality control of image reference monitors for medical institutions; and undertakes contract development of embedded systems, such as printers and communication equipment, various business systems, medical examination systems, etc., as well as portal website construction, server environment design / construction / operation / maintenance, simple visual inspection equipment, etc. In addition, it offers systems development solutions, such as support for corporate IT-related services, including building systems comprising hardware and software procurement; solutions and support for IT, personnel, and security in the fields of temporary staffing, system development, and PC recycling; and business system development and IT support through a lean system development system, as well as staffing for system engineering and back office, PC data deletion, and recycling services. The company was formerly known as RealVision Inc. and changed its name to RVH Inc. in April 2015. RVH Inc. was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
